title: How Did Cassie's Surgery Go?
description:
A few weeks ago, Cassie opened up about her doctor's not taking her seriously about a problem she was having. Finally she found a doctor that was able to diagnose what she has. Because of this diagnosis, she had to have surgery. How'd it go? We have an update!
